channel.title: A serious problem
channel.description: I'm 16, male, and I'm sexually active with one person. This person has a very high sex drive and wants to have sex a lot. I have a very low sex drive and don't want to have sex very much at all. Yes, we have sex, but I don't really enjoy it, I just do it to please her. What do I do? I'm not very experienced and she has had plenty of experience. I don't know how to talk dirty, and of course she wants me to. I just don't know what to do. I would rather cuddle and kiss than have sex, but with her that always leads to sex. She gets turned on so easily. I doubt this is normal for a 16 year old guy...
